ca.ualberta.cs.lonelytwitter

Class Tweet

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cs.lonelytwitter.Tweet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tweetable, java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImportantTweet, NormalTweet

    public abstract class Tweet
extends java.lang.Object
implements Tweetable, java.lang.Comparable
    Abstract representation of a Tweet (see Twitter.org for some idea of what this is). This implementation has no consideration for the user that tweets the tweet.
    See Also:
    LonelyTwitterActivity, TweetTooLongException, Mood
